== 毒物 ==
貓的{{link-en|毒素排解|detoxification}}（detoxification）能力低於[[人類|人類]]與[[狗|狗]]等動物，因此有許多普通的家中的物品，對貓而言可能具有危險性<ref name="judy" /><ref name="vetinfo" />。舉例而言，常見的止痛劑[[撲熱息痛|撲熱息痛]]（商品名包括泰諾林、普拿疼等），即使在對人類安全的劑量下<ref name="CanVetJ2003-Allen">{{cite journal en| author = Allen AL | title = The diagnosis of acetaminophen toxicosis in a cat | journal = Canadian Veterinary Journal | year = 2003 | pages = 509-10 | volume = 44 | issue = 6 | id = PMID 12839249 | url = http://www.pubmedcentral.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pubmed&pubmedid=12839249}}</ref><ref name="vetinfo" />，也可對貓產生嚴重毒害，因為貓缺乏代謝這些藥物的酵素。若貓有攝取到這些藥物的可能，則必須立即接受獸醫師治療<ref name="VetHumToxicol1998-Villar">{{cite journal en| author = Villar D, Buck WB, Gonzalez JM | title = Ibuprofen, aspirin and acetaminophen toxicosis and treatment in Dogs and Cats | journal = Vet Hum Toxicol | year = 1998 | pages = 156-62 | volume = 40 | issue = 3 | id = PMID 9610496}}</ref>。即使是能用來治療發生於貓身上之[[關節炎|關節炎]]的[[阿斯匹林|阿斯匹林]]，對貓的毒性也比人類更大<ref name="vetinfo" />。而用來對抗掉毛的[[敏諾西代|敏諾西代]]（商品名為[[落建|落建]]），對貓也可能致命<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Camille DeClementi | coauthors = Keith L. Bailey, Spencer C. Goldstein, and Michael Scott Orser | title = Suspected toxicosis after topical administration of minoxidil in 2 cats | journal = Journal of Veterinary Emergency and Critical Care | pages = 287–292 | volume = 14 | issue = 4 | id = {{doi|10.1111/j.1476-4431.2004.04014.x}} | accessdate= 2007-01-18|date=December 2004}}</ref><ref>{{cite web en | url = http://www.showcatsonline.com/x/minoxidil.htm | title = Minoxidil Warning | accessdate = 2007-01-18 | publisher = ShowCatsOnline.com | quote = Very small amounts of Minoxidil can result [in] serious problems or death | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070103001500/http://showcatsonline.com/x/minoxidil.htm | archivedate = 2007-01-03 }}</ref>。多種[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]與[[除草劑|除草劑]]也有危險性，其他可能對貓產生毒害的家庭常見用品，還有[[樟腦丸|樟腦丸]]等[[萘|萘]]類化學製品<ref name="vetinfo" />，以及以[[苯酚|苯酚]]製成，如[[六氯酚|六氯酚]]、[[滴露|滴露]]等多種[[清潔劑|清潔劑]]<ref name="vetinfo">{{cite web en | url = http://www.vetinfo4cats.com/ctoxin.html | title = Toxic to Cats | accessdate = 2007-01-18 | publisher = Vetinfo4Cats | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080103204216/http://www.vetinfo4cats.com/ctoxin.html | archive-date = 2008-01-03 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author = Rousseaux CG, Smith RA, Nicholson S | title = Acute Pinesol toxicity in a domestic cat | journal = Vet Hum Toxicol | year = 1986 | pages = 316-7 | volume = 28 | issue = 4 | id = PMID 3750813 | url= http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&db=PubMed&list_uids=3750813&dopt=Abstract}}</ref>。對人類有毒的[[抗凍劑|抗凍劑]][[乙二醇|乙二醇]]，即使只有一小匙，也可能使貓死亡<ref>{{cite web en|url=http://www.cfainc.org/articles/antifreeze.html |title=Antifreeze Warning |publisher=The Cat Fanciers' Association, Inc. |accessdate=2007-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620095612/http://www.cfainc.org/articles/antifreeze.html |archivedate=2009-06-20 }}</ref>。除了上述藥劑，許多家中栽種的植物<ref name="judy">{{cite web en | url = http://www.judyshealthcafe.com/articles/substances.html | title = Substances That Are Poison to Pets | accessdate = 2007-01-18 | publisher = Judy's Health Cafe.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070206040257/http://www.judyshealthcafe.com/articles/substances.html | archive-date = 2007-02-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>、普通的人類食物，對貓也有毒性，如[[巧克力|巧克力]]中[[可可鹼|可可鹼]]；相對大量的[[洋蔥|洋蔥]]與[[大蒜|大蒜]]也對貓有害<ref name="vetinfo" />。若貓居住地有[[百合屬|百合屬]]植物，就算貓不舔食這些植物，也有腎衰竭風險。

